description: The view from the top of the castle is breathtaking.  As you step out onto the half-enclosed roof, you get the feeling of being on top of the world.  A Wehnimer's flag flutters in the breeze atop the east towers, and a large cannon stands at the ready, its barrel pointed toward the sea.  A large wooden tub sits in the center of the rooftop, filled to the brim with bubbling water.  Obviously the guards who man this post enjoy their comfort during peaceful times.
title: [Helden Hall, Rooftop]
